    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Raman\u2019s maths teacher is very strict . He gave Raman a very difficult task to be completed by tomorrow . The task is as follows: \nA tree with n vertices is given .The ith of N-1 edges connects ai and bi Every vertex has  Ai number of candies stored on it.  Raman can perform the following operation.<br><br>\n\u2022\tSelect a pair of different leaves x and y. Remove exactly one candy from each vertex in the path from x to y .<br><br> \nAnd the task is to determine wheather it is possible to remove all the candies performing the given operation any no. of times. Note that the operation can not be performed if there is a vertex with zero candies in the path.\nAs he has other important important tasks to do , he want you to solve this task for him.\n</p>\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p>First line contains an integer N . Next line has an array A having N integers.  Next N-1 lines describes the edges of the tree.</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p>If it is possible to remove all the stones from the vertices, print YES. Otherwise, print NO.</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<p>Should contain all the constraints on the input data that you may have. Format it like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>2</b> \u2264 <b>N</b> \u2264 <b>100000</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>ai,bi</b> \u2264 <b>N</b></li>\n<li><b>0</b> \u2264 <b>Ai</b> \u2264 <b>1000000000</b></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input:</b>\n5\n1 2 1 1 2\n2 4\n5 2\n3 2\n1 3\n\n<b>Output:</b>\nYES\n</pre>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n",
